						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1458 (mistake for 1478), Rākshasa, Jyēshṭha, ba. 10</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1555 June 14, Friday</hi> (not verifiable) in the reign of <hi rend="bold">Sadāśivarāya.</hi> It records that <hi rend="bold">Timmarāja,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Dombara-Timarāja,</hi> made a gift for the service of a god (name lost), for the prosperity of his family.</p>						

						<p>First Face.</p>						

